---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<head>
  <title>Rene Mireles</title>
</head>

<Layout>
  <section id="hero" class="mb-60">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center px-5vw py-32">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-title text-4xl">YO SOY</h3>
        <h1 class="text-center font-title text-9xl font-bold">RENE MIRELES</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-10 flex gap-4">
        <img src="cristal.svg" alt="decoration" class="w-3" />
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium">Disenador / Ilustrador</h2>
        <img src="cristal.svg" alt="decoration" class="w-3" />
      </div>
      <p class="mb-16 text-center text-3xl leading-relaxed opacity-50">
        Ayudo a duenos de negocios a mejorar la identidad de sus marcas al crear
        disenos que les ayuden a transmitir su mensaje claramente y de manera
        creativa.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#projects"
        class="rounded-md bg-purple-100 px-14 py-8 font-title text-4xl font-bold transition-colors hover:bg-purple-200"
      >
        VER PORTAFOLIO
      </a>
    </div>
    <img
      src="rene-paint.png"
      alt="Painting of this websites creator"
      class="w-full"
    />
  </section>
  <section id="skills" class="mb-60">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-14 px-5vw py-32">
      <h1 class="text-center font-title text-9xl font-bold">MIS HABILIDADES</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-3xl leading-relaxed opacity-50">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy
        eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam
        voluptua. At vero eos et accusam et justo
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-3xl leading-relaxed opacity-50">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy
        eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam
        voluptua.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img
      src="skills.png"
      alt="Painting of this websites creator"
      class="w-full"
    />
  </section>
  <section id="projects" class="mb-60">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-14 px-5vw py-32">
      <h1 class="text-center font-title text-9xl font-bold">
        PROYECTOS RECIENTES
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-3xl leading-relaxed opacity-50">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy
        eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam
        voluptua. At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores et ea rebum. Stet
        clita kasd gubergren, no sea takimata sanctus est Lorem ipsum dolor sit
        amet. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr,
      </p>
      <div class="h-60 w-full bg-purple-200"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="contact" class="mb-60">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-14 px-5vw py-32">
      <h1 class="text-center font-title text-9xl font-bold">CONTACTO</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-3xl leading-relaxed opacity-50">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy
        eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam
        voluptua. At vero eos et accusam et justo
      </p>
      <form action="" method="post" class="flex flex-col gap-14 w-full">
        <label
          for="nombre"
          class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full font-bold text-3xl"
          >Nombre
          <input
            type="text"
            name="nombre"
            id="nombre"
            class="h-20 p-5 rounded-md"
          />
        </label>
        <label for="email" class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full font-bold text-3xl"
          >Email
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            id="email"
            class="h-20 p-5 rounded-md"
          />
        </label>
        <label
          for="message"
          class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full font-bold text-3xl"
          >Mensage
          <input
            type="text"
            name="message"
            id="message"
            class="h-60 p-5 rounded-md"
          />
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="rounded-md bg-purple-100 px-14 py-8 font-title text-4xl font-bold transition-colors hover:bg-purple-200"
          >ENVIAR</button
        >
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
